Doc: An entity for defining the master confirmation agreement executed between the parties.

Source.Contents:
/#
   An entity for defining the master confirmation agreement executed between the parties.
 #/
record FpML5.recordkeeping.MasterConfirmation {
  # The type of master confirmation executed between the parties.
  masterConfirmationType : string?

  # The date of the confirmation executed between the parties and intended to govern all relevant transactions between those parties.
  masterConfirmationDate : date?

  # The date that an annex to the master confirmation was executed between the parties.
  masterConfirmationAnnexDate : date?

  # The type of master confirmation annex executed between the parties.
  masterConfirmationAnnexType : string?

}

masterConfirmationType.Doc: The type of master confirmation executed between the parties.
masterConfirmationType.Name: masterConfirmationType

masterConfirmationDate.Doc: The date of the confirmation executed between the parties and intended to govern all relevant transactions between those parties.
masterConfirmationDate.Name: masterConfirmationDate

masterConfirmationAnnexDate.Doc: The date that an annex to the master confirmation was executed between the parties.
masterConfirmationAnnexDate.Name: masterConfirmationAnnexDate

masterConfirmationAnnexType.Doc: The type of master confirmation annex executed between the parties.
masterConfirmationAnnexType.Name: masterConfirmationAnnexType
